WEBVTT

00:01:58.806 --> 00:02:01.374
is because we've all decided they should.

00:02:01.398 --> 00:02:03.227
And because we've decided that,

00:02:03.251 --> 00:02:04.420
they do.

00:02:05.223 --> 00:02:09.363
Money is about the exchanges
and the transactions

00:02:09.387 --> 00:02:11.448
that we have with each other.

00:02:12.042 --> 00:02:14.850
Money isn't anything objective.

00:02:14.874 --> 00:02:19.271
It's about a collective story
that we tell each other about value.

00:02:20.101 --> 00:02:21.482
A collective fiction.

00:02:22.170 --> 00:02:25.053
And that's a really powerful concept.

00:02:26.059 --> 00:02:27.526
In the past two decades,

00:02:27.550 --> 00:02:29.819
we've begun to use digital money.

